<item>
            <title>[LU-1304] MDS restructuring</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1304</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Remove the last uses of non-portable storage APIs in the Lustre Release 2.0 metadata stack and update existing use of the OSD API to the new transaction model.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
